# Owner dashboard and menu editor

Read **agents.md** sections on menu editor and owner dashboard editing.

## File size

Thousands of lines with inline subcomponents. Search for the tab or label you need — do not read the entire file.

## Menu editor rules

- Load menu once on mount — do not poll getMenu on the analytics refresh interval
- While unsavedChanges is true, never overwrite menuItems from a server fetch
- Save is explicit (Save Changes button); show loading during fetch and during save
- Category rename marks unsaved state — does not auto-persist to database
- Always save the complete in-memory menu tree; partial state can wipe images, SKU, or dishes

## Dashboard refresh

Analytics, subscriptions, and tickets may poll on an interval — menu data is excluded from that poll.

## Plus tier

Gate premium features with the existing paywall modal pattern; default tier is FREE.

Preserve inline component pattern unless extraction clearly reduces duplication.
